2899 - Chemicals and Chemical Preparations, Not Elsewhere Classified Summary > Chemetall (Australasia) Pty Ltd is a manufacturer and supplier of surface treatment chemicals for the general and aerospace industries. The company is a local operating subsidiary of Chemetall GmbH, a German aerospace and surface treatment company. Globally, Chemetall is a leading supplier of surface technologies, and operates 22 production locations and more than 40 branch offices worldwide. The company services clients in the aerospace and military, aluminium, food, general industry, non destructive testing and surface finishing industry. Chemetall (Australasia) is headquartered in the eastern Melbourne suburb of Bayswater North, Victoria. The companyâ€™s Melbourne-based manufacturing facility is supported by distribution operations in all Australian states and territories.
